nk":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.GaugeGroupQuot","kind":"inductive","line":164,"name":"StandardModel.GaugeGroupQuot","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L164-L177"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₃\"><span class=\"name\">StandardModel</span>.<span class=\"name\">GaugeGroupℤ₃</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The gauge group of the Standard Model with a ℤ₃-quotient, i.e., the quotient of `GaugeGroupI` by\nthe ℤ₃-subgroup `gaugeGroupℤ₃SubGroup`.\n\nSee https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₃","kind":"def","line":155,"name":"StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₃","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L155-L162"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.gaugeGroupℤ₃SubGroup\"><span class=\"name\">StandardModel</span>.<span class=\"name\">gaugeGroupℤ₃SubGroup</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The ℤ₃-subgroup of the un-quotiented gauge group which acts trivially on all particles in the\nstandard model, i.e., the ℤ₃-subgroup of `GaugeGroupI` derived from the ℤ₃ subgroup of\n`gaugeGroupℤ₆SubGroup`.\n\nSee https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.gaugeGroupℤ₃SubGroup","kind":"def","line":145,"name":"StandardModel.gaugeGroupℤ₃SubGroup","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L145-L153"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₂\"><span class=\"name\">StandardModel</span>.<span class=\"name\">GaugeGroupℤ₂</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The gauge group of the Standard Model with a ℤ₂ quotient, i.e., the quotient of `GaugeGroupI` by\nthe ℤ₂-subgroup `gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup`.\n\nSee https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₂","kind":"def","line":136,"name":"StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₂","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L136-L143"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup\"><span class=\"name\">StandardModel</span>.<span class=\"name\">gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The ℤ₂subgroup of the un-quotiented gauge group which acts trivially on all particles in the\nstandard model, i.e., the ℤ₂-subgroup of `GaugeGroupI` derived from the ℤ₂ subgroup of\n`gaugeGroupℤ₆SubGroup`.\n\nSee https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup","kind":"def","line":126,"name":"StandardModel.gaugeGroupℤ₂SubGroup","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L126-L134"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\" title=\"declaration uses 'sorry'\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₆\"><span class=\"name\">StandardModel</span>.<span class=\"name\">GaugeGroupℤ₆</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The smallest possible gauge group of the Standard Model, i.e., the quotient of `GaugeGroupI` by\nthe ℤ₆-subgroup `gaugeGroupℤ₆SubGroup`.\n\nSee https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₆","kind":"def","line":118,"name":"StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₆","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L118-L124"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\" title=\"declaration uses 'sorry'\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.gaugeGroupℤ₆SubGroup\"><span class=\"name\">StandardModel</span>.<span class=\"name\">gaugeGroupℤ₆SubGroup</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">inst</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#Group\">Group</a> <a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.GaugeGroupI\">GaugeGroupI</a></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Subgroup/Defs.html#Subgroup\">Subgroup</a> <a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/Basic.html#StandardModel.GaugeGroupI\">GaugeGroupI</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The subgroup of the un-quotiented gauge group which acts trivially on all particles in the\nstandard model, i.e., the ℤ₆-subgroup of `GaugeGroupI` with elements `(α^2 * I₃, α^(-3) * I₂, α)`,\nwhere `α` is a sixth complex root of unity.\n\nSee https: